Package ml.karmaconfigs.lockloginmodules.shared.listeners.events.plugin

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    MigrationRequestEvent
    This event is fired when a player or the console types migrate command, with an invalid argument, for example /locklogin migrate Hello.
    PluginProcessCommandEvent
    This event is fired when a player or server performs a LockLogin command ( $[argument] )
    PluginStatusChangeEvent
    This event is fired when the plugin status changes, from PluginStatusChangeEvent.Status.LOAD to PluginStatusChangeEvent.Status.UNLOAD, PluginStatusChangeEvent.Status.RELOAD_START to PluginStatusChangeEvent.Status.RELOAD_END, or PluginStatusChangeEvent.Status.UPDATE_START to PluginStatusChangeEvent.Status.RELOAD_END
  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description
    PluginStatusChangeEvent.Status
    Available plugin status
